<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    {{>upperlinks}}
    <title>Humata</title>
</head>

<body>
    {{>nav}}
    <div class="intro">
        <h1>Humata: AI Tool Overview</h1>
        <div class="read-word"></div>
        <div class="count-word"></div>
      <p>Humata is an artificial intelligence (AI) platform that uses machine learning and natural language processing to assist
    businesses and organisations make better decisions.
    It is a platform designed to make the usage of AI as simple and user-friendly as possible, enabling users to simply
    construct, deploy, and integrate AI models into their current processes.</p>
    <p>Humata's capacity to analyse massive volumes of data and get actionable insights from it is one of its primary
    strengths.
    Humata can analyse enormous volumes of data and offer useful insights and suggestions to its consumers by utilising
    cutting-edge machine learning algorithms and natural language processing techniques.
    Because of this, it is the perfect tool for companies and other organisations trying to acquire a competitive edge
    through data-driven decision-making.</p>
    <p>Along with offering strong data analysis capabilities, Humata also has an easy-to-use interface that makes working with
    AI models straightforward for users.
    The platform contains a variety of pre-built models that may be quickly incorporated into current processes, as well as
    a drag-and-drop interface for creating and training machine learning models.
    This makes it simple for customers to start utilising the tool and start reaping the rewards of AI-driven
    decision-making, even if they have little or no prior expertise with AI.</p>
    <p>The flexibility of Humata to integrate with a variety of other tools and platforms is another crucial aspect.
    The platform may be coupled with a variety of different tools and systems, such as data storage platforms, business
    intelligence tools, and more. It is designed to be very versatile and configurable.
    Because of this, users may simply integrate AI into their current workflows without having to significantly alter their
    current systems and procedures.</p>
    <p>To sum up, Humata is a strong and adaptable AI platform that gives companies and organisations the capacity to make
    data-driven decisions and acquire a competitive edge.
    Humata makes it simple for businesses to start utilising the advantages of AI and obtain a deeper knowledge of their
    data thanks to its user-friendly interface and ability to link with other tools and platforms.</p>
    </div>








    <script>
        const paragraphs = document.querySelectorAll(".intro p");
        const readTimeDiv = document.querySelector(".read-word");
        const count = document.querySelector(".count-word");

        const calculatedReadTime = () => {
            let numberOfWords = 0;
            const averageWPM = 265;

            paragraphs.forEach(paragraph => {
                numberOfWords += paragraph.innerHTML.split(" ").length;
            })

            let readTime = numberOfWords / averageWPM;

            readTimeDiv.innerHTML = Math.round(readTime) + " minute read"
            count.innerHTML = numberOfWords + " -words approximate"

        }
        calculatedReadTime();



    </script>

    {{>lowerlinks}}
</body>

</html>